A very basic bluetooth logger.

Logs to the sqlite file btlog.db which defaults to be in /var/lib/misc

See configure.ac

schema:

create table log (
        id integer primary key autoincrement,
        mac char(17),
        name varchar(100),
        seen integer );

Create a new db using sqlite3 -init the_schema_file btlog.db

Move it to /var/lib/misc.

To see what is happening when running build with debug mode:

./configure --enable-debug

More options etc later.

